<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Activation</title>
</head>

<body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333333;">
    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%"
        style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px; background-color: #007bff; text-align: center;">
                <h1 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; margin: 0;">Welcome!</h1>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Hello {{name}},</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Thank you for registering with us. To activate your account, please use
                    the following activation code:</p>
                <div
                    style="background-color: #f8f8f8; border: 1px solid #e1e1e1; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <h2 style="font-size: 24px; color: #007bff; margin: 0;">{{activationCode}}</h2>
                </div>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #777777; font-style: italic;">If you did not register for an
                    account, please disregard this email.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; color: #777777;">
                <p style="margin: 0;">If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>